Sure, here are some examples:

1. Ona *sprema* doručak. (She is preparing breakfast.)
2. Mama me uči kako se *sprema* tijesto. (Mom is teaching me how to prepare dough.)
3. Oni *spremaju* kuću za proslavu. (They are preparing the house for the celebration.)
4. Kada se *spremamo* za put, uvijek zaboravimo nešto. (When we prepare for a trip, we always forget something.)
5. *Spremi* svoje stvari, idemo. (Pack your things, we're leaving.)
6. On *sprema* iznenađenje za svoju djevojku. (He is preparing a surprise for his girlfriend.)
7. Nije mi jasno kako ona uspijeva sve *spremiti* na vrijeme. (I don't understand how she manages to prepare everything on time.)
8. Moramo se *spremiti* za zimu. (We have to prepare for winter.)

I hope this helps!